# Action menu stuff (left panel, with hotbars etc)

ui-actionmenu-function-lock-action-slots = (Un)lock dragging and clearing action slots
ui-actionmenu-function-open-abilities-menu = Open Action Menu

ui-actionmenu-error-no-more-than-8 = You can't have any more than 8 main actions. Clear some by right-clicking them to make room.
ui-actionmenu-error-insufficient-skills = You can't recall how to do that...
ui-actionmenu-error-attempt-non-main-action = That doesn't quite come to you off the top of your head... Make it a main action.